me nulle part dans lalittérature.\end{remark}%\begin{verbatim}%"[...] While the naturality of the invariants is a classical result which%appears in many textbooks I could not find the compatibility properties of%Theorem 2.5.10(b), (c) in the literature. [...]"%\end{verbatim}%*******************************************************************************\ifx\indiplome\undefined	\end{document}\fi\endinput